<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(يَحْسِبُهُ الجاهل ما لم يَعْلَمَنْ ... )</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
